This paper discusses a method for evaluating the impact of UI design languages on mobile app ratings and installs, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also involves data analysis, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of UI components in different app categories, which could fall under cybernetics (cs.CY) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
